ews" Kano State Ministry of Health has confirmed that it recorded the first patient who died of coronavirus in the state. April 16, 2020 In "News" By David Royal The Nigeria Centre for Disease Control, NCDC, on Saturday via its verified Twitter handle announced that the deadly virus, known as coronavirus (COVID-19) has spread to 19 states in the country. The centre also confirmed that 10 people have died from the virus since the outbreak in… April 12, 2020 In "Coronavirus Updates"